      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "@finnw Are you sure that the encoding is UTF-16BE and not UTF-16? According to the String class Javadoc (<a href=\"https://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/String.html\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/lang/String.html</a>), &quot;A String represents a string in the UTF-16 format...&quot;."
    }, {
