      "creation_date" : 1727361547,
      "post_id" : 4387559,
      "comment_id" : 139343521,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "No longer true since Java 9, <a href=\"https://openjdk.org/jeps/254\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">openjdk.org/jeps/254</a>, where ASCII-only Strings are now internally encoded as a <code>byte[]</code> with a single byte per character."
